Nadar () is a rural locality (a selo) in Tlyaratinsky Selsoviet, Tlyaratinsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:
Geography
Nadar is located 1&nbsp;km southeast of Tlyarata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Tlyarata is the nearest rural locality.
